snippet.title: Cosmo Duel CBT Match 3 Games Free For Android
snippet.description:
Join Cosmo Duel gamers worldwide in this epic match 3 puzzle journey through the cosmos! 

Create massive bombs by combining more blocks of the same color, or transform energy into special items. Strategize your every move to clear stages and defeat your opponents!

Experience stellar battles
● Explore the cosmos and enjoy peaceful single play
● Duel players from all around the world, in real time!

Mix and match to win
● Use energy to create massive explosions
● Place items strategically to increase your combos and score
● Earn stars and unlock new stages, avatars, and items!

Collect the cosmos' most charismatic avatars
● Choose between 8 unique avatars and their outfits
● Unlock special skills unique to each avatar
● Personalize your chat with different emoji!

Genre(s) : Puzzle
Subcategories : Match 3 Games Free
Require internet connection : Yes (Online)
Size :  92 MB
Date Released : 2018-01-18
Platforms: Android
Developed By : GAMEVIL Inc. 
Languages : English
Requirements: 5.0 and up

Google Play download Cosmo Duel URL:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gamevilusa.cosmoduel.android.google.global.normal

Thanks for every Like and Favorite! They really help!
